    items={[
      {
        title: "To <b>empower</b> students",
        description:
          "I want our club to bring the very best out of people, allowing them to build great things without anything to slow them down.",
      },
      {
        title: "To <b>impact</b> others",
        description:
          "I want to be able to create a tangable impact on the world what we do (in a positive way), which includes reaching out to the local community",
